channel.title: Compile help plz!
channel.description:
(im not that good at rsps's)ive been editing my server which is allstar scape v2 i go to client edit it and the go to compile
it says:
client.java:11407: cannot find symbol symbol : variable action location: class client c.action = 1; ^ client.java:11445: cannot find symbol symbol : variable action location: class client c.action = 0; ^ Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 2 errors Files Compiled Successfully! Press any key to continue . . .
how do i find where the error is??

item.title: Compile help plz!
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

Use code tags. a cannot find symbol error means what it says. your trying to call something but when it compiles the compiler can’t match your call with the name your using. Check to see what your action is really named. it could be something else.
